com.github.mhdirkse.countlang.lang

Interface CountlangListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CountlangBaseListener, CountlangListenerDelegator

    public interface CountlangListener
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
    This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by CountlangParser.
